    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因英国减税和移民政策面临保守党的强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党宣言的早期草案引发了外界不安，人们担心该宣言缺乏可能避免保守党在英国大选中惨败的重大承诺。内阁大臣们在最后一刻呼吁里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在宣言中添加新的减税措施和更严格的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
