      <title>亨特·拜登的辩护因枪支案而中断，无需证词</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登在特拉华州因枪支指控受审，陪审团未能就其在吸毒期间非法购买枪支的指控迅速做出裁决。他们预计将于周二恢复审议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:08:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
