      <title>欧盟选举加剧政治风险 新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元走弱，波动性指标上升，因为随着极右翼在欧洲选举中的进展，政治风险成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</guid>
